title: Projected annual inflation rate in the United States 2010 to 2024
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Inflation rate. In total the number of data points it has is 15.
In general Inflation rate has rose over the Year.
Inflation rate is roughly constant from 2010 to 2014, slightly increasing from 2014 to 2016, and finally roughly constant from 2016 to 2024.
The highest Inflation rate, of value 3.14 was reached at Year 2011
Minimum Inflation rate about 0.12 was reached at Year 2015
